        <Parent_String>salons (rooms for entertaining) [300004459], social and sitting spaces [300004388], rooms and spaces by function [300004021], rooms and spaces [300133704], built work divisions [300072553], components by specific context [300241584], components (objects parts) [300241583], Components (hierarchy name) [300241490], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
