    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Drawing rooms in private houses as distinguished from a 'salon de famille;' designated as a meeting place for guests and found only in houses where the primary drawing room is so large that a more intimate space is required.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
